data.description: Welcome to this charming, one and half story, country-feeling home sitting on over an acre of land on the west side of Kokomo! Inside you will find four bedrooms, two full baths, a spacious dining and living room, a neutral canvas and tons of natural light. Enjoy the open front porch, four car garage and all the space this property also offers outdoors. You can easily walk to the trails and parks nearby.  Recent updates include new roof, new water heater.
